Uses node-irc client: https://node-irc.readthedocs.io/en/latest/index.html

A 'conf' folder should be created in the root directory and it should contain a 'conf.json' file.

conf.json example:

{
  "irc": {
    "server": "irc.pretome.info",
    "username": "PreToMeUserName",
    "password": "NickServIdentifyPassword",
    "opts": {
      "userName": "PreToMeUserName",
      "realName": "????",
      "autoConnect": true,
      "autoRejoin": true,
      "retryCount": 100,
      "retryDelay": 10000,
      "encoding": "UTF-8"
    },
    "lastDisconnectFile": "last_disconnect.log"
  }
}
